--- !u!114 &1476954644
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1476954643}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a2b878c1b0778e244aa3bd0e9970ed64, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _dialogueManager: {fileID: 1737419913}
  _dialogue:
  - Character:
      CharacterName: ???
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: 'Ah, you must be the captain of the research vessel, Ocean Why. '
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "I\u2019m Thamsin, the researcher whom you\u2019ll be assisting for the
      day."
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "I see that you\u2019re familiar with two of your compatriots, so I won\u2019t
      bother you with their introductions.  "
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "Anyways, we\u2019re near an area of interest where a new specimen is reportedly
      sighted."
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "However, there are issues with the oxygen canisters. They\u2019ve appeared
      to be empty at the moment. "
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "So you\u2019ll be filling them. Don\u2019t worry, I\u2019ll guide you
      through the process."
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "Also, I have been receiving reports of a specific electrical breaker not
      functioning and the reactor being unstable.\r"
  - Character:
      CharacterName: Thamsin
      Portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c434818d4eae24749855d034a4bbeddb, type: 3}
      PortraitOffset: {x: -400, y: 0}
      PortraitScale: 10
    Text: "Please quickly address those two issues before we proceed to the vessel's
      reactor.\r\r"
